{
  "number": 70,
  "name": "سُورَةُ المَعَارِجِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Ma'aarij",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "A supplicant asked for a punishment bound to happen",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "To the disbelievers; of it there is no preventer.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "[It is] from Allah, owner of the ways of ascent.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "The angels and the Spirit will ascend to Him during a Day the extent of which is fifty thousand years.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "So be patient with gracious patience.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "Indeed, they see it [as] distant,",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "But We see it [as] near.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "On the Day the sky will be like murky oil,",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "And the mountains will be like wool,",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And no friend will ask [anything of] a friend,",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 568,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "They will be shown each other. The criminal will wish that he could be ransomed from the punishment of that Day by his children",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "And his wife and his brother",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "And his nearest kindred who shelter him",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And whoever is on earth entirely [so] then it could save him.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "No! Indeed, it is the Flame [of Hell],",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "A remover of exteriors.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "It invites he who turned his back [on truth] and went away [from obedience]",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "And collected [wealth] and hoarded.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 227,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Indeed, mankind was created anxious:",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "When evil touches him, impatient,",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "And when good touches him, withholding [of it],",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Except the observers of prayer -",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Those who are constant in their prayer",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "And those within whose wealth is a known right",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "For the petitioner and the deprived -",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "And those who believe in the Day of Recompense",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And those who are fearful of the punishment of their Lord -",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "Indeed, the punishment of their Lord is not that from which one is safe -",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And those who guard their private parts",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "Except from their wives or those their right hands possess, for indeed, they are not to be blamed -",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "But whoever seeks beyond that, then they are the transgressors -",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And those who are to their trusts and promises attentive",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "And those who are in their testimonies upright",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "And those who [carefully] maintain their prayer:",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "They will be in gardens, honored.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 502,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "So what is [the matter] with those who disbelieve, hastening [from] before you, [O Muhammad],",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "[To sit] on [your] right and [your] left in separate groups?",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "Does every person among them aspire to enter a garden of pleasure?",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "No! Indeed, We have created them from that which they know.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 569,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "So I swear by the Lord of [all] risings and settings that indeed We are able",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "To replace them with better than them; and We are not to be outdone.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "So leave them to converse vainly and amuse themselves until they meet their Day which they are promised -",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "The Day they will emerge from the graves rapidly as if they were, toward an erected idol, hastening.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Their eyes humbled, humiliation will cover them. That is the Day which they had been promised.",
      "juz": 29,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 570,
      "ruku": 503,
      "hizbQuarter": 228,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}